                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14729202" author="apachespark" created="Thu, 3 Sep 2015 15:03:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;liancheng&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/8586&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/8586&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14729445" author="davies" created="Thu, 3 Sep 2015 17:39:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lian+cheng&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lian cheng&quot;&gt;lian cheng&lt;/a&gt; I think it&apos;s hard to guarantee forward computability (former version can read data generated by new version), do we really need this change?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14730326" author="lian cheng" created="Fri, 4 Sep 2015 05:04:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s true that in general forwards-compatibility is not easy to guarantee, but to this specific case, compatibility is broken by an unfortunate typo rather than any reasonable design decision.  However, this probably shouldn&apos;t block 1.5.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rxin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rxin&quot;&gt;rxin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14730388" author="lian cheng" created="Fri, 4 Sep 2015 06:36:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Another concern of mine is that, Parquet files written by a version of Spark will stay there unchanged. Reducing possible corner cases to handle brings benefits in the long run.  Ideally, I still would like to have this one in 1.5, of course, only if we would have another RC.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14731917" author="lian cheng" created="Sat, 5 Sep 2015 09:51:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Issue resolved by pull request 8586&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/8586&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/8586&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
